<li class='cover' id='bookCover_278105'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/278105.Squeeze_Play"><img alt="Squeeze Play" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1175793683l/278105.jpg" />
